        <li><strong>Aloe Fresh S2 (6.5 mg):</strong> Mint softened with aloe — uniquely herbal.</li>
        <li><strong>Frozen Mint Superslim S4 (8 mg):</strong> Slender pouch, bold cooling effect.</li>
        <li><strong>Intense Spearmint Ice S4 (11.3 mg):</strong> Sharper spearmint with icy bite.</li>
        <li><strong>Intense Peppermint Ice S4 (11.3 mg):</strong> Peppermint for a punchier, warmer mint profile.</li>
