    <h2>Final Thoughts</h2>
    <p>Skruf is the thinking user's brand. It doesn't shout; it delivers. Heritage, consistent quality, flavour diversity, and a tiered strength system that respects user progression. If you're tired of Instagram marketing and viral gimmicks, Skruf's 20+ years of craft refinement will feel like coming home.</p>
    <p>Try Fresh Mint S3 first. If mint doesn't move you, explore Purple Cassice or Nordic Licorice. You'll understand why Swedish users never left.</p>

